{"tid":1941931,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人記得喵斗之拳，喵巴?","createTime":"2020-03-24T17:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T06:12:37.000Z","uid":119080,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"94a32ef1011ec56eeccb5a50cb9de1cd924d6a32","tid":1941931,"uid":119080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T17:50:08.000Z","msg":"屌講起呢條精神科神棍病人就好撚好笑<br />\n當年睇佢個POST講到自己出神入法咁 上天入地 在家中通靈 乜鳩耶穌 佛祖<br />\n好似好耐無見到佢d post 彈出熱門 唔知佢死左味<br />\n講到自己咁神又唔見佢用鍵盤發功消滅肺炎病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母 閒日無事就吹吹吹 成撚個智障兒咁<br />\n信佢個d都唔知係咪弱能學校畢業出黎<br />\n<br />\n成撚個玄燊師傅咁 用風水算命配合勵志故事 日撚日係youtube彈出廣告<br />\n真係唔撚係佢日撚日彈出廣告我都唔撚上黎屌鳩佢<br />\n玄燊師傅係勁就唔洗咁等錢洗 日日賣廣告啦屌你<br />\n算命都仲要分ABCD PLAN 屌你老母 做撚埋補習天王啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080cd09f8e6572b7387ead8b41eb55268cb0b234","tid":1941931,"uid":36383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T00:23:44.000Z","msg":"你屌喵巴? 小心比大量連登仔咬"},{"pid":"b564edf9c74333c51a2409fc15b58d28391160eb","tid":1941931,"uid":347211,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T01:14:34.000Z","msg":"喵巴鬼鬼地"},{"pid":"32679ecd702d767114dff82e538654f7eb9d3f33","tid":1941931,"uid":12421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T05:02:55.000Z","msg":"記得之前有個人喺啲你問我答post話自己喺神社做過神主<br />\n<br />\n條垃圾喵又彈出嚟話通過安倍靖明知佢係真料<br />\n<br />\n但後尾樓主俾人篤爆咗係假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b6183b1d10830cdb1f68d566e465a4f489bd5b","tid":1941931,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32679ecd702d767114dff82e538654f7eb9d3f33","tid":1941931,"uid":1